hw2

library(readr)

bs <- read_csv("book.csv")
## Parsed with column specification:
## cols(
##   .default = col_character(),
##    = col_integer(),
##    = col_double(),
##    = col_double(),
##    = col_integer()
## )
## See spec(...) for full column specifications.
lon.deg <- sapply((strsplit(as.character(bs$""), ",")), as.numeric)
lat.deg <- sapply((strsplit(as.character(bs$""), ",")), as.numeric)
bs$lat <- lat.deg
bs$lon <- lon.deg

library(ggmap)
## Loading required package: ggplot2
map_4 <- get_map(location = c(lon = 120.5, lat = 23.625), zoom = 8)
## Map from URL : http://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=23.625,120.5&zoom=8&size=640x640&scale=2&maptype=terrain&language=en-EN&sensor=false
ggmap(map_4) + geom_point(aes(x = lon, y = lat), data = bs)

library(readr)

bs <- read_csv("book.csv")
## Parsed with column specification:
## cols(
##   .default = col_character(),
##    = col_integer(),
##    = col_double(),
##    = col_double(),
##    = col_integer()
## )
## See spec(...) for full column specifications.
lon.deg <- sapply((strsplit(as.character(bs$""), ",")), as.numeric)
lat.deg <- sapply((strsplit(as.character(bs$""), ",")), as.numeric)
bs$lat <- lat.deg
bs$lon <- lon.deg

library(ggmap)
map_4 <- get_map(location = c(lon = 120.5, lat = 23.625), zoom = 8)
## Map from URL : http://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=23.625,120.5&zoom=8&size=640x640&scale=2&maptype=terrain&language=en-EN&sensor=false
ggmap(map_4) + geom_point(aes(x = lon, y = lat, size = ""), data = bs)

ggmap(map_4, darken = c(0.5, "white")) +
  geom_point(aes(x = lon, y = lat, size = ""), data = bs)
